Class RecordKeyManager

  suncertify.db.RecordKeyManager
public final class RecordKeyManager
extends java.lang.Object

Provides the same record key object and reuses the key. Caches the record id as an Integer and reuses the same instance.

getKey

public static java.lang.Integer getKey(int recNo)
Returns a cached key object given the record number. If a cached key is not available then a new one is created and returned. The first hit also adds the key to the cache of keys.

Parameters:
recNo - The record number to lookup.
Returns:
The record key.
